Ques 01 — Online Shopping Cart System.

Project Overview
-----------------
Develop a Spring Core application to manage shopping cart details using setter injection.

Classes
-------
Product: productId, name, price
Cart: cartId, userName, product (dependency)

System Description
------------------
The cart holds product details which are injected using setter methods configured in XML.

Real-Time Scenario
-------------------
Used in e-commerce applications where users add products to cart dynamically.
